{"tid":1069340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冚家鏟］拒絕讓郭家麒提緊急質詢　梁君彥：不符「性質急切」條件","createTime":"2019-03-20T02:00:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T02:12:22.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12c529ba745d467b2ccd477110c563adcb938acc","tid":1069340,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:00:34.000Z","msg":"立場報道2019/3/19 &mdash; 21:31<br />\n<br />\n港鐵測試新訊號系統期間發生列車相撞意外，公民黨郭家麒要求在明日（20日）的立法會大會上提出急切質詢。不過他今日接獲立法會秘書處回覆，指立法會主席梁君彥認為事件不屬「性質急切」，拒絕緊急質詢要求。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒今日在 FB 公開立法會秘書處回覆。秘書處引述梁君彥指，港鐵已公開表示事故由新信號系統的軟件問題引致，與現有系統無關，港鐵亦已全面暫停新系統測試，政府亦指出現有系統獨立於新系統，因此是安全的。梁君彥認為，事件的急切程度未達至必須在明日立法會上提出，不符合「性質急切」的條件，因此不批准緊急質詢要求。<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒則在FB中，留下「主席繼續護主心切 」、「總之同公眾有重大關係嘅就無急切性」、「港人生命何價」的標籤以表不滿。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥任內極少接納議員提出緊急質詢的要求。去年10月港鐵「四綫齊冧」，梁君彥罕有批准新民主同盟范國威在大會上提出急切口頭質詢，是他在今屆會期至今唯一一次批准緊急質詢要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/港鐵相撞-拒絕讓郭家麒提緊急質詢-梁君彥-不符-性質急切-條件/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E8%AE%93%E9%83%AD%E5%AE%B6%E9%BA%92%E6%8F%90%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E6%80%A7%E8%B3%AA%E6%80%A5%E5%88%87-%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%2F&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9DH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=69449821\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E7%9B%B8%E6%92%9E-%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E8%AE%93%E9%83%AD%E5%AE%B6%E9%BA%92%E6%8F%90%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6-%E6%80%A7%E8%B3%AA%E6%80%A5%E5%88%87-%E6%A2%9D%E4%BB%B6%2F&h=bbf84ff8\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/港鐵相撞-拒絕讓郭家麒提緊急質詢-梁君彥-不符-性質急切-條件/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd8f3054d611fee927a970143043ec07859263c6","tid":1069340,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"條友都唔坐地鐵既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw以前成日見到曾鈺成坐火車地鐵"},{"pid":"a6648e03fffeae3cad86f849d4cdb077b4a53ff6","tid":1069340,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd8f3054d611fee927a970143043ec07859263c6","tid":1069340,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"條友都唔坐地鐵既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw以前成日見到曾鈺成坐火車地鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"佢條躝坦根本連議事規則都可能未讀得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9736194faf0696236a4b9bc720f309577093296a","tid":1069340,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6648e03fffeae3cad86f849d4cdb077b4a53ff6","tid":1069340,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd8f3054d611fee927a970143043ec07859263c6","tid":1069340,"uid":22609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:03:18.000Z","msg":"條友都唔坐地鐵既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw以前成日見到曾鈺成坐火車地鐵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:07:18.000Z","msg":"佢條躝坦根本連議事規則都可能未讀得晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:12:22.000Z","msg":"係議會乜都做唔到邊個最開心？<br />\n梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}